Text: Compaq ClassicDear Jeff I would personally like to invite you to this years Compaq Classic in New Orleans May The ProAm is played at the famous English Turn course on Wednesday May and already we have a commitment that Jack Nicklaus will be there along with many of our customer and partner CEOs I simply wanted to drop you a quick note but you will receive a separate electronic invitation very soon I know we havent had a chance to get together but I hope we can make arrangements to meet very soon Please call my office if you have any questions Hope you can join us Michael Capellas Chairman CEO Compaq
